[gunshot]

1103
01:32:08.329 --> 01:32:09.096
[gunshot]

1104
01:32:13.467 --> 01:32:15.002
[Bunny]
<i>Zeus. we're leaving. mate.</i>

1105
01:32:15.069 --> 01:32:16.137
Coming to ya.

1106
