What the fuck does that mean?

1130
01:34:42.816 --> 01:34:44.553
It means there is no extract.

1131
01:34:45.052 --> 01:34:46.720
There's no one coming for them.

1132
01:34:52.693 --> 01:34:53.727
What the hell happened
